{"word":"G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee - Feign","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hypokrínomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Feign"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்பி, நடி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to take up another's statements in reference to what one has decided for oneself"},{"paragraph":"2. to make answer (speak) on the stage, to personate anyone, play a part"},{"paragraph":"3. to simulate, feign, pretend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919 - κρίνω - krínō - kree'-no/2919\">G2919</a>; to <i>decide</i> (<i>speak</i> or <i>act</i>) <i>under</i> a false part, that is, (figuratively) <i>dissemble</i> (<i>pretend</i>): - feign."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4942 - συνυποκρίνομαι - synypokrínomai - soon-oo-pok-rin'-om-ahee/4942\">G4942</a>, <a href=\"#/G505 - ἀνυπόκριτος - anypókritos - an-oo-pok'-ree-tos/505\">G505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee/5271\">G5271</a>, <a href=\"#/G5272 - ὑπόκρισις - hypókrisis - hoop-ok'-ree-sis/5272\">G5272</a>, <a href=\"#/G5273 - ὑποκριτής - hypokritḗs - hoop-ok-ree-tace'/5273\">G5273</a>"}]}